 sport car in which he travelled from Southampton to Milan. We spent together with him some time in Milan and in San Remo.

We both send our love to all three of you.





Yours ever,

V

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: GLENWAY WESCOTT1

CC, 1 p.





Hotel Astoria

Menton (A.M.)

France

February 7, 1960

Dear Mr. Wescott,

